Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將本該由我解決的大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉的宇智波佐助也不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被一雙不錯的眼睛給盯上了 阿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波鼬在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來就放你們一條生路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫輪眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙果然是鼬的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幹掉大蛇丸也多虧了宇智波一族的血統 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個繼承了優良血統的自以為是的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先解決一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要問問你這多嘴的傢伙關於鼬的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼呢 阿飛 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為他是小鬼就掉以輕心啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的瞬身之術太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是避不開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先用查克拉等級C1來試探他的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿飛 快點退後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前…前輩 暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能喊「喝」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 後面後面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他是個嚴苛的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是個很好的前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對…不會忘記迪達拉前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喋喋不休的煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手掌來製造出爆炸物的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算靠著爆風逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好輸入的查克拉只是C1而已 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的動作實在是太快了 這些又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微陪你玩一下吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙小孩的玩意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該動手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒什麼大不了的 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿飛 你到底是哪邊的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還真是挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在用C2應該是最適合的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩最擅長的藝術之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C2龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧 阿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要做那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就使用那個吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大傢伙 也能變成爆炸物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了 阿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且從形狀來看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從空中來嗎 這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他見識一下前輩流行藝術的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行藝術已死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的可是超級平面藝術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誘導彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先解決那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來伸長的極限是5米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊距離被看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是卡卡西的那招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能伸縮也能投擲的形態變化還真不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟之前的威力可不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是大蛇丸的咒印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連翅膀都長出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠飛起來躲過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 地雷粘土已經全部安置妥當了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 阿飛 你離遠一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有誘導彈 下面有地雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C2就是以地雷妨礙對手行動 然後從空中準確地轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這協作攻擊就是其關鍵點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳邊已經埋下了密密麻麻的地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需踩到便會自動爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓誘導彈確實地命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意飛到接近我攻擊範圍極限的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那受傷的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成功躲避我從空中進行的攻擊嗎 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是特大號的哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會讓你飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你用翅膀做盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經飛不起來了吧 只剩一邊翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是迪達拉前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下能結束戰鬥了吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西怎麼可能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有立足點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入地雷陣裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會被炸得七零八落的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立足點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 竟然被他夠到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持不了平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙故意把刀插進地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來確認有沒有地雷 從而製造出立足點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倚靠作為立足點的刀的長度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以單翼進行跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 剛剛的攻擊只是為了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我逼到刀子的正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣查克拉刀就能以最短的距離…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 下面是地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果最後你還是被炸死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉前輩這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓你不要廢話囉嗦了 阿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…混賬小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我鑒賞藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要這種小鬼跟我搭檔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢是不錯 但這傢伙可是容易早死的類型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是首領的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的能力可以派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道我的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在近鄰各國間協助反國家分子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開爆炸恐怖襲擊的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個逃亡忍者做那種事的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的 才沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是接受他人的委託去引發爆炸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是我的作品 嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這造型是以精煉的線條追求二次元變形的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是個藝術品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的藝術不只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作品是流動的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有外形的東西僅僅是個造型物 嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這個會爆炸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸會讓它的存在得到昇華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能成為我真正的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會在那一瞬間的昇華中感覺到藝術 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術就是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 還是我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙眼睛是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟我交手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了 你就要加入曉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忍術可是崇高的藝術 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受藝術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼囂張的樣子 也就這種程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是看清楚自己的樣子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就要自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是容易早死的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術嗎 什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始的時候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你看見鼬的寫輪眼之時 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經身處幻術之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然會對別人的能力著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比他厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕不輸給任何人的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更加厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可能會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然把起爆粘土給吃掉了 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我的絕招 接下來就要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿飛 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了 是C4迦樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這是為了殺鼬而準備的術 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳 藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的尾聲 迪達拉的究極絕招終於爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來阻止鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自不同的思想相互交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村陷入最大的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村子的命令就必須服從 這是規定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將卡卡西老師的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與村民們的性命放在天平上去衡量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版 火影忍者疾風傳 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
